@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### 기술 스택 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "name": "Java",
  "category": "LANGUAGE",
  "proficiency": "ADVANCED",
  "yearsOfExp": 3
}

### 기술 스택 생성 실패
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/999999/tech-stacks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "name": "",
  "category": "LANGUAGE",
  "proficiency": "ADVANCED",
  "yearsOfExp": 3
}

### 기술 스택 전체 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks

### 기술 스택 단건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks/1

### 존재하지 않는 기술 스택 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks/999999

### 기술 스택 페이징 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks?page=0&size=5

### 기술 스택 조건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks?category=LANGUAGE&proficiency=ADVANCED

### 기술 스택 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "proficiency": "INTERMEDIATE",
  "yearsOfExp": 5
}

### 기술 스택 수정 실패
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks/999999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "proficiency": "INTERMEDIATE"
}

### 기술 스택 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks/1
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

### 기술 스택 삭제 실패
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1/tech-stacks/999999
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken
